{"Sid":0,"Did":25468,"Id":"312289","Title":"周德榮訪談錄","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/collection/2020-01-04/20dbcd1b-28fe-4a2c-9f39-d2afe2c8660c/p1.29-DSC_3517.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Object","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n周德榮（原名周德容），民國19年6月19日出生；浙江省嘉興縣人。\n\n早期父親擔任鹽務局長，抗戰時，鹽務局跟著孫立人將軍後撤逃難，逃往貴州才安定下來。\n\n抗戰勝利後，轉往香港，民國35年又到北京、東北唸書。後又隨著孫立人來臺，便居住於黃埔新村，後輾轉至屏東師專唸書。民國40年結婚。然因，孫立人案的爆發，使得原先跟著孫立人過來臺灣的老部屬，均受到牽連，其中黃埔新村不少人受到牽連，而遭到刑求。\n\n周德容為當時期的見證者，受訪者一直在國小教書，直到退休。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"NULL","Keyword_Latitude":"NULL","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/object/7652F4D6-798D-4D81-807B-51B4594AA549","Original_Identifier":"312289","Keyword_Subject_1":"社會與政治","alias":"","alternativeHeadline":"","Keywords":"黃埔新村 / 誠正國小 / 鳳山","dates":"採訪時間 / 2018/05/24","LastUpdateTime":"2020/01/04 16:38:51","Creator":"顧超光、程景秀","publisher":"","mediaType":"文件","language":"","timelines":"戰後時期 (1945~)","city":"高雄市鳳山區","address":"","lng":"","lat":"","contributors":"","contributor":"顧超光、程景秀","size":"","admin":"","award":"","character":"","contentLocation":"","acquireWay":"","acquireSource":"","storage":"","version":"","isbn":"","onlineAuthLink":"","stuff":"","url":"","createOrgName":"高雄市政府文化局","citation":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/collectionOpen/2020-01-04/1cf11cad-9eab-490d-b8d5-1021a9f4ca0b/p1.29-DSC_3517.jpg"}}